metadata.description: Celebrate VIP Memberships are a collection of 10,000 exclusive membership cards that will be minted upon purchase and will live on the ethereum blockchain. This Membership card will give you exclusive access to our marketplace, lifetime access to pre mint future NFT projects, Access to our CelebrateNFT DAO, VIP Lounge, and enters you into the most insane roadmap of giveaways and multiverse celebrations along the way
